be right for the spot.

1265
00:37:51,169 --> 00:37:51,870
-[snoring].

1266
00:37:55,574 --> 00:37:56,442
-Oh, god.

1267
00:37:59,445 --> 00:38:01,680
-My father's a garbage man
in New York for 40 years.

1268
00:38:01,780 --> 00:38:02,581
He comes out to Hollywood.

1269
00:38:02,681 --> 00:38:03,682
He's got a bigger
career than me.

1270
00:38:03,782 --> 00:38:04,916
-Yeah.

1271
00:38:05,016 --> 00:38:06,352
