00:38:07,686 --> 00:38:08,387
-What?

1274
00:38:08,487 --> 00:38:09,220
No.

1275
00:38:09,321 --> 00:38:11,357
I had a salami sandwich before.

1276
00:38:13,992 --> 00:38:14,693
-Salami?

1277
00:38:14,793 --> 00:38:15,527
-Star material, no?

1278
00:38:15,627 --> 00:38:16,662
-Yeah.

1279
00:38:16,762 --> 00:38:18,697
