00:38:36,982 --> 00:38:38,149
We're here.

1294
00:38:38,249 --> 00:38:39,084
Hi.

1295
00:38:39,184 --> 00:38:39,918
-Hi, Daddy.

1296
00:38:40,018 --> 00:38:40,719
Hi, Daddy.

1297
00:38:40,819 --> 00:38:41,252
-Daddy.

1298
00:38:41,353 --> 00:38:41,887
-Hi, there.

1299
00:38:41,987 --> 00:38:42,721
Hey, sweetie.

1300
00:38:42,821 --> 00:38:43,655
-Can I be up first?
-Yeah.

1301
00:38:43,755 --> 00:38:44,456
Yeah.

1302
00:38:44,556 --> 00:38:45,457
Go-- uh, give me a second.

1303
00:38:45,557 --> 00:38:46,024
-OK.

1304
00:38:46,124 --> 00:38:47,225
-Hey, Anthony.

1305
00:38:47,325 --> 00:38:48,694
Twice around the bases
on the double, all right?

1306
00:38:48,794 --> 00:38:50,696
-You know, I spoke
with Dorian earlier.

1307
00:38:50,796 --> 00:38:53,064
And, uh, he asked me
if I had talked to you.

1308
00:38:53,164 --> 00:38:54,666
And I told him I hadn't.

1309
00:38:54,766 --> 00:38:57,235
And he dropped it, like
it wasn't important.

1310
00:38:57,335 --> 00:38:59,270
Which made me think right
away something was up.

1311
00:38:59,371 --> 00:39:00,071
-Really?

1312
00:39:00,171 --> 00:39:01,272
-Yeah, really.

1313
00:39:01,373 --> 00:39:04,410
And now you start in with
this weird eye thing.

1314
00:39:04,510 --> 00:39:08,213
You want to tell me what
the hell's going on or not?

1315
00:39:08,313 --> 00:39:09,715
-Nothing.

1316
00:39:09,815 --> 00:39:11,450
