liar on the planet.

1319
00:39:15,186 --> 00:39:15,954
I'm hurt, man.

1320
00:39:16,054 --> 00:39:16,755
Really.

1321
00:39:16,855 --> 00:39:18,123
I am really hurt.

1322
00:39:18,223 --> 00:39:20,592
