1336
00:39:34,440 --> 00:39:35,073
It's me.

1337
00:39:35,173 --> 00:39:36,742
It's Steve.

1338
00:39:36,842 --> 00:39:39,645
-You got to promise not to
get into the actor envy thing.

1339
00:39:39,745 --> 00:39:42,313
Not on this one, please?

1340
00:39:42,414 --> 00:39:43,449
-Oh, god.

1341
00:39:43,549 --> 00:39:47,986
